# ChangeLog for net-dns/pdns-recursor
# Copyright 1999-2013 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2

*pdns-recursor-3.5.2 (18 Jun 2013)

  06 Jul 2013; Thomas D. <whissi@whissi.de> +pdns-recursor-3.5.2-r1.ebuild,
  -pdns-recursor-3.5.2.ebuild:
  * Init script renamed to pdns-recursor
  * Init script improved
    * Init script will now use Gentoo's built-in start/stop/status function
    * Stop function is now more reliable due to pidfile usage
    * Added additional commands like reload_acls, reload_zones
      top_remotes and get_all
  * Improved chroot support

*pdns-recursor-3.5.2 (18 Jun 2013)

  18 Jun 2013; Thomas D. <whissi@whissi.de> +pdns-recursor-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.
